  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>This course will provide you with an introduction to both the creative and technical aspects of creative media production. It will also encourage personal development enabling you to acquire the skills, knowledge and understanding to progress to further education and employment within the creative industries.</p>]]></mainContent>
